{"tid":1121780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"心很累","createTime":"2019-04-23T14:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T14:05:35.000Z","uid":205450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8164ec778448383541a5f9ca46e4892f4da28abb","tid":1121780,"uid":205450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"若要生活好 咪撚讀Civil <br />\n呢句係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年小弟year 1 準備就讀完第2個sem<br />\n呢科真係chur撚到仆街 啲科又多到戇鳩鳩<br />\n其他系一個sem都係讀5,6科 <br />\n戇鳩鳩今個sem我要讀成8,9科 人都癲<br />\n一個禮拜爆堂冇day off <br />\n想搵part time返吓同抖吓嘅時間都冇<br />\n心好累 自己畢咗業之後又唔係想做工程師<br />\n揀呢科嘅原因純粹因爲中學我數學同物理成績好<br />\n完全對工程冇乜興趣<br />\n讀埋佢又好似哂時間 <br />\n唔讀好似哂個一年錢 又唔知自己做乜撚嘢好<br />\n為讀而讀咁 毫無人生方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打可以打救吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}